{"tid":352630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"腦細叫我返埋今日就算","createTime":"2017-08-09T02:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T07:53:48.000Z","uid":67261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f404bd19e9ef4033a1f383e780a2216303138ccd","tid":352630,"uid":67261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:06:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的  我岩岩轉工 見工個陣 dept個主任都有份見<br />\n見完之後佢行埋黎拍我膊頭話睇好我 想我快啲就職<br />\n我見呢度好似好好發圍 咁咪果斷比錢 辭左之前份舊工<br />\n點知依家返到兩個月零三日 佢無啦啦叫我入房，話有野斟。<br />\n咁好啦，我以為有咩帶"},{"pid":"cca960de9339742adf1e29ca26a83115eb3d942d","tid":352630,"uid":67261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:11:46.000Z","msg":"我以為有咩帶挈 <br />\n點知佢同我講做埋今日唔洗返 <br />\n我就問點解<br />\n佢話: 佢日日都痾幾次屎   其實痾屎唔緊要 你做到野   但係啊姐成日投訴有人痾到啲屎後面廁板位周圍都係 <br />\n我反應都黎唔切  哦左一聲就出返去做野<br />\n但我依家諗深一層  冇可能係我 我有少少潔癖 每次痾完都自己抹一次廁板 今舖真係明屈  我可以點算好<br />\n利申: 依家痾緊屎"},{"pid":"d379ee430ab257ef9af7a93e4f2889047d53f844","tid":352630,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053db83b3be21116ec597c625236f2c7d7f2bbca","tid":352630,"uid":8081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80dd8fdfe0c02da4e5721b9b109bbb2fd9242eff","tid":352630,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"佢屙屎關你撚事"},{"pid":"642703d28edb74a5a0ff03a5ce7a17a4356ca874","tid":352630,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:52:44.000Z","msg":"你哦就算你傻架？"},{"pid":"582f4eab73cc234ffa4eebb60c40afa092686b0a","tid":352630,"uid":67261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"我向腦細澄清左  佢話延長我試用"},{